sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / kubectl
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as OGX Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS<br/>service-serving-cert
    participant Operator as OGX Operator Manager<br/>8080/8081/TCP
    participant OCI as OCI Image Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OGXServer as OGX Server Instance<br/>8321/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,OGXServer: Flow 1: OGXServer CR Creation & Validation

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply OGXServer CR<br/>Auth: User credentials
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-ogx-io-v1beta1-ogxserver<br/>HTTPS/9443, TLS (service-serving-cert)<br/>Auth: API server CA
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response<br/>(validates distribution, provider IDs,<br/>model refs, adoption annotations)
    K8sAPI-->>User: CR accepted / rejected

    Note over User,OGXServer: Flow 2: OGXServer Reconciliation

    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event: OGXServer created/updated<br/>HTTPS/6443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Operator->>OCI: Fetch OCI labels for base config<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Registry credentials
    OCI-->>Operator: OCI manifest labels<br/>(base config resolution)

    Note over Operator: Generate config.yaml from<br/>base config + declared providers<br/>(inference, vector I/O, tools, files)

    Note over Operator: Render kustomize manifests:<br/>Deployment, Service, PVC, NetworkPolicy,<br/>PDB, HPA, Ingress, ServiceAccount,<br/>ConfigMap (content-hash, immutable)

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Patch resources (SSA)<br/>HTTPS/6443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Resource status

    Note over Operator: Poll OGX Server health

    Operator->>OGXServer: GET /v1/health<br/>HTTP/8321 (configurable)<br/>Auth: None (in-cluster)
    OGXServer-->>Operator: Health status
    Operator->>OGXServer: GET /v1/providers<br/>HTTP/8321
    OGXServer-->>Operator: Provider info
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Patch OGXServer/status<br/>HTTPS/6443

    Note over User,OGXServer: Flow 3: Legacy Resource Adoption<br/>(LlamaStackDistribution → OGXServer)

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Read LlamaStackDistribution resources<br/>HTTPS/6443
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Legacy Deployment, PVC, Service, Ingress

    Note over Operator: Scale legacy Deployment to 0<br/>Wait for pod termination<br/>(prevents RWO PVC multi-attach)

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Scale legacy Deployment → 0 replicas<br/>HTTPS/6443
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Transfer PVC ownership (no ownerRef)<br/>Transfer Service/Ingress selectors<br/>HTTPS/6443
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Adoption complete
